### Health
GET http://localhost:4000/health

### Markets
GET http://localhost:4000/markets

GET http://localhost:4000/markets/stats

### Snapshot (adjust symbol/timeframe as needed)
GET http://localhost:4000/snapshot?symbol=BTC/USDT&timeframe=1h
GET http://localhost:4000/snapshot?symbol=BTC/USDT&timeframe=4h

### Auth
POST http://localhost:4000/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "demo@example.com",
  "password": "changeme",
  "walletAddress": "0x0000000000000000000000000000000000000000"
}

### Replace <token> with returned JWT
GET http://localhost:4000/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer <token>

### Portfolio upsert
POST http://localhost:4000/portfolio/holdings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "wallet": "0x0000000000000000000000000000000000000000",
  "assetSymbol": "BTC",
  "quantity": 0.1,
  "averageCost": 30000
}

### Portfolio fetch
GET http://localhost:4000/portfolio/holdings?wallet=0x0000000000000000000000000000000000000000

### Wallet balances (configure WALLET_TOKEN_LIST or reward token)
GET http://localhost:4000/wallet/balances?address=0x0000000000000000000000000000000000000000

### Premium status
GET http://localhost:4000/premium/status?address=0x0000000000000000000000000000000000000000

### Rewards
GET http://localhost:4000/rewards/epoch/latest
GET http://localhost:4000/rewards/history?address=0x0000000000000000000000000000000000000000
GET http://localhost:4000/rewards/proof?address=0x0000000000000000000000000000000000000000

### AI chat summary
POST http://localhost:4000/ai/chat
Authorization: Bearer <token>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "What's the outlook?",
  "symbol": "BTC/USDT",
  "timeframe": "1h",
  "horizonMinutes": 60
}

### AI direct inference (requires JWT + access pass)
POST http://localhost:4000/ai/infer
Authorization: Bearer <token>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "symbol": "BTC/USDT",
  "timeframe": "1h",
  "horizonMinutes": 60,
  "candles": [],
  "indicators": []
}

### AI backtest (requires JWT + access pass)
POST http://localhost:4000/ai/backtest
Authorization: Bearer <token>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "symbol": "BTC/USDT",
  "timeframe": "1h",
  "horizonMinutes": 60,
  "candles": [],
  "indicators": []
}

### External proxies
GET http://localhost:4000/external/coingecko/market?ids=bitcoin,ethereum
GET http://localhost:4000/dex/spot?chainId=1&sellToken=0xA0b86991c6218b36c1d19d4a2e9eb0ce3606eb48&buyToken=0xC02aaA39b223FE8D0A0e5C4F27eAD9083C756Cc2
Accept: application/json

###

GET http://localhost:4000/dex/pool/reserves?chainId=1&poolAddress=0x397FF1542f962076d0BFE58eA045FfA2d347ACa0
Accept: application/json

### Billing price
GET http://localhost:4000/billing/price?chainId=31337

### Billing purchase (requires JWT and wallet with ACT balance)
POST http://localhost:4000/billing/purchase
Authorization: Bearer <token>
